{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"maprequestcontext\">\n<span id=\"id1\"></span><h1>mapRequestContext</h1>\n<p>Transforms the <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">RequestContext</span></tt> before it is passed to the inner route.</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"signature\">\n<h2>Signature</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">mapRequestContext</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">RequestContext</span> <span class=\"k\">\u21d2</span> <span class=\"kt\">RequestContext</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Directive0</span> \n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"description\">\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>The <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">mapRequestContext</span></tt> directive is used as a building block for <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../advanced-topics/custom-directives/#custom-directives\"><em>Custom Directives</em></a> to transform\nthe request context before it is passed to the inner route. To change only the request value itself the\n<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../mapRequest/#maprequest\"><em>mapRequest</em></a> directive can be used instead.</p>\n<p>See <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../#request-transforming-directives\"><em>Directives transforming the request</em></a> for an overview of similar directives.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"example\">\n<h2>Example</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">val</span> <span class=\"n\">probe</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span> <span class=\"nc\">TestProbe</span><span class=\"o\">()</span>\n<span class=\"k\">val</span> <span class=\"n\">replaceResponder</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">mapRequestContext</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">_</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">copy</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">responder</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">probe</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ref</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">val</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">replaceResponder</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">complete</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;abc&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"nc\">Get</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;/abc/def/ghi&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">handled</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"kc\">false</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n<span class=\"n\">probe</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">expectMsgType</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">HttpMessagePartWrapper</span><span class=\"o\">].</span><span class=\"n\">messagePart</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"nc\">HttpResponse</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">entity</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span> <span class=\"nc\">HttpEntity</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;abc&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": true, "title": "mapRequestContext", "sourcename": "", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "documentation/spray-routing/basic-directives/mapRequestContext", "next": {"link": "../mapRouteResponse/", "title": "mapRouteResponse"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["documentation/spray-routing/basic-directives/mapRouteResponse", "mapRouteResponse", "N", "next"], ["documentation/spray-routing/basic-directives/mapRequest", "mapRequest", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Documentation"}, {"link": "../../", "title": "spray-routing"}, {"link": "../../predefined-directives-by-trait/", "title": "Predefined Directives (by trait)"}, {"link": "../", "title": "BasicDirectives"}], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">mapRequestContext</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#signature\">Signature</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#description\">Description</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#example\">Example</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../mapRequest/", "title": "mapRequest"}, "metatags": ""}